        <div n="578-76L6" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="underline">By Dr </hi>Swift<hi rend="underline">, and not published among his works</hi>.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>ITH undigested thoughts opprest,</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-2"> I sunk from reverie to rest.</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-3"> An horrid vision seiz'd my head;</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-4"> I saw the graves yawn up their dead;</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-5"> Jove arm'd with terrors op'd the skies,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-6"> The thunder roars, and lightning flies;<gap/><gap/></l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-7"> While each pale spectre hangs its head,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-8"> Jove nodded, burst the clouds, and said,──<gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/></l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-9"> “You whom the various sex have shamm'd,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-10"> And come to see each other damn'd,</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-11"> As priests have threaten'd (tho' they knew</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-12"> No more of my decrees than you)</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-13"> The world's vain business now being o'er,</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-14"> Such dogmas may prevail no more;</l><l n="15" xml:id="spp-578-76L6-line-15"> I 'gainst such blockheads set my wit,<hi rend="underline">I d────you all</hi>!──Go, go, you're bit.”578-76L6   </l></lg></div>
      </div>
